Mark Truscott and I

32:10.362 --> 32:13.165
went to college together.

32:13.199 --> 32:15.067
He's not the only person
at the FDA

32:15.101 --> 32:17.736
who has a stake in QuoVadis.

32:17.769 --> 32:20.372
Take out your company phone.

32:24.476 --> 32:26.012
