from China.

33:02.014 --> 33:04.516
Top medical device companies

33:04.550 --> 33:07.653
all use products from China.

33:07.686 --> 33:09.855
And label it
"made in the USA"?

33:09.888 --> 33:11.290
Others did exactly that.

33:11.323 --> 33:14.660
This is fraud.
Outright fraud.

33:14.693 --> 33:16.962
How in God's name did you think
you'd get away with this?

33:16.995 --> 33:18.230
I'm not getting away
with anything.

33:18.264 --> 33:20.366
They're safe,
safe as any others.

33:20.399 --> 33:22.034
Your heart valve killed people.

33:22.068 --> 33:25.204
You are not a team player.

33:30.876 --> 33:33.379
I signed
a nondisclosure agreement.

33:33.412 --> 33:37.583
I-I can't tell anyone
what I know.

33:37.616 --> 33:40.719
If you just let me go, I...

33:40.752 --> 33:42.588
I'll disappear.

33:44.223 --> 33:46.425
I gave you
the golden opportunity

33:46.458 --> 33:48.994
to get into the future
of health care.

33:49.027 --> 33:51.463
To make a fortune.

33:54.300 --> 33:57.303
Do you know what I hate
the most in this world?

34:00.272 --> 34:02.274
Betrayal.

34:12.084 --> 34:14.086
You made it.

34:15.587 --> 34:17.989
I wouldn't miss it
for the world.

34:19.258 --> 34:22.861
-I'm gonna say hi to Micah.
-Mm-hmm.

34:22.894 --> 34:25.264
Where's your date?

34:25.297 --> 34:29.101
Oh, well, I plan on meeting
the love of my life here.

34:29.135 --> 34:30.969
It happens at weddings,
you know?

34:31.002 --> 34:32.438
Mm-hmm.

34:35.807 --> 34:36.975
MICAH:
Wow.

34:37.008 --> 34:38.910
This looks awesome.

34:38.944 --> 34:42.080
I am dying for these saris.
I want all of them now.

34:42.114 --> 34:44.883
-It's all so romantic.
-Ugh, wake me
when the ceremony is over.

34:44.916 --> 34:46.718
I take it you're eloping.

34:46.752 --> 34:49.388
Why get married if you don't
want kids? And I don't.

34:49.421 --> 34:50.889
At least, not for
the foreseeable future.

34:50.922 --> 34:52.424
Yeah, me, neither.

34:53.492 --> 34:55.394
You don't want kids?

34:55.427 --> 34:56.962
-I already have a child.

34:56.995 --> 34:58.964
My sister, Jessie.

35:01.600 --> 35:04.736
Hey. You're not on call.
None of us are.

35:04.770 --> 35:07.072
Guys, let's turn off our phones.

35:07.105 --> 35:09.141
Ooh, that's a radical move.

35:09.175 --> 35:12.744
One of life's greatest events.
Birth, death, marriage.

35:12.778 --> 35:14.180
AUSTIN:
And we should honor it.

35:16.382 --> 35:19.451
Hey, guys.
Any of you seen Devon?

35:35.000 --> 35:36.635
I need to speak to Priya.

35:36.668 --> 35:39.004
Uh, you can't. It's bad luck.

35:39.037 --> 35:42.308
Hey, Priya

35:42.341 --> 35:44.310
Devon?

35:44.343 --> 35:46.478
What are you doing here?

35:49.881 --> 35:51.717
Can we have a minute, please?

35:52.984 --> 35:54.553
Mm.

36:02.361 --> 36:04.230
You look great.

36:04.263 --> 36:05.931
So do you.

36:07.399 --> 36:12.137
The most beautiful
I have ever seen you.

36:12.170 --> 36:15.241
What's this about?

36:15.274 --> 36:16.908
We've been together
for three years.

36:16.942 --> 36:18.810
And four months.

36:18.844 --> 36:22.881
And I've loved you
all that time.

36:22.914 --> 36:26.652
And, just as important,
I've respected you.

36:26.685 --> 36:30.689
And that's why I have
to tell you the truth.

36:33.392 --> 36:36.495
Recently, I've been attracted
to somebody else.

36:36.528 --> 36:40.198
I didn't sleep with her,
but I did kiss her.

36:40.232 --> 36:45.237
It's-it's over, and I'm never
gonna see her again.

36:47.439 --> 36:52.043
I tried to put it behind me,

36:52.077 --> 36:54.713
but I can't.

36:57.416 --> 36:59.585
I can't marry you.

36:59.618 --> 37:03.289
Not when I have feelings
for somebody else.

37:05.457 --> 37:09.060
You deserve somebody
that loves you,

37:09.094 --> 37:10.596
and only you.

37:11.997 --> 37:15.367
It would be wrong,

37:15.401 --> 37:17.636
for the both of us.

37:18.904 --> 37:20.806
Your timing sucks.

37:22.841 --> 37:24.209
I realize.

37:24.242 --> 37:26.211
Everyone's here.

37:26.244 --> 37:28.914
Family came from India,
from Boston, from England.

37:28.947 --> 37:32.217
I know, but do we go through
with it because of that?

37:32.250 --> 37:34.620
Why did you wait until now
to tell me?

37:34.653 --> 37:37.556
Because I thought
it was nothing.

37:37.589 --> 37:40.392
Some last-minute panic attack.

37:40.426 --> 37:42.661
But I realize now

37:42.694 --> 37:44.830
