for this person.

37:44.863 --> 37:47.833
I'll do whatever
you tell me to do.

37:47.866 --> 37:50.802
I'll talk to everyone. I'll talk
to both parents. It's on me.

37:53.271 --> 37:56.608
You've humiliated me,

37:56.642 --> 38:00.579
