gets you off the hook?

38:00.612 --> 38:03.349
No, no, I... no, I don't. I...

38:03.382 --> 38:07.285
I'm-I'm ashamed of myself
for hurting you.

38:07.319 --> 38:10.656
But lying or not telling you
would be worse.

38:13.892 --> 38:16.328
Priya.

38:16.362 --> 38:17.963
Please, I'm...

38:17.996 --> 38:20.632
Who are you?

38:20.666 --> 38:22.601
Not the man I loved.

38:22.634 --> 38:25.671
Get out. I never want
to see you again.

38:25.704 --> 38:27.506
Get out!

38:51.763 --> 38:55.033
